About Bitdeer:
Bitdeer Group is the world's leading digital asset mining ecological service provider. It was founded by Jihan Wu, a renowned pioneer in the crypto industry, along with Sequoia Capital, IDG, and other well-known investment institutions in the field of blockchain. Bitdeer Group was established in 2020 with the headquarter in Singapore and has branches across the globe such as the United States, Europe, and other countries and regions. Adhering to a professional, authentic, and reliable corporate culture, Bitdeer Group is committed to becoming the world's most reliable digital asset mining service provider, which can provide customers with full mining eco-services including computing power sharing and mining farm management.
About the team
We are the MiningCloud team, mainly including the sale of cloud computing power and cloud hosting products, as well as mining agent-related services. Our team's mission is to reflect computing power fluctuations and yield curves of each order the most intuitive and true, So that users can recognize our products, trust our services, and ultimately get greater benefits. We believe your success is our goal and passion at Bitdeer.
What you will be responsible for:
Responsible for the technical architecture, business model design and R & D of the platform back-end system;
Solve the technical difficulties and performance tuning in project development;
Responsible for the training of technical personnel and the team's technical training;
Work with business department, product and test team to split tasks, ensure code quality and project success.
How you will stand out:
Bachelor degree or above, major in computer science or other related fields;
More than 3 years of Java development experience, deep understanding and application of Java technology stack;
Familiar with SpringBoot, SpringMVC, MyBatis and other mainstream development frameworks;
Familiar with Cache, MQ, MySQL and other technologies, have rich experience in background performance optimization;
Strong capability in coding and system design. A problem solver for technical problems, possess experience managing small-scale project development team, able to lead the development team to carry out development work;
Familiar with microservice framework, such as SpringCloud, k8s etc. will be at advantage.
What you will expect:
Fast-growing digital assets service provider company with a supreme network of investors, pioneers and enthusiast with ample knowledge and experience in the new industry;
Ability to contribute directly and make an impact to the future of digital asset industry;
The chance to build up new things/processes/systems from scratch;
Personal accountability, fast growth and learning opportunities;
An inspiring working environment with dynamic workspaces, flexible work time, flat structures,?great team and a start-up spirit
Attractive salary package and welfare benefits.
The change to grow your knowledge and career with internal and external training and mentoring resources.

